desc: Choice Meat Market is Los Angeles #1 Quality and Taste butcher in Koreatown. We specialize in KBBQ as well as Prime, Kobe, Muji, Style Meats. Our most popular meats are Ribeye, Brisket, Steak, Pork Jowl, Pork Belly, Bulgogi, Kkotsal, Galbi, and Beef Short Ribs. We also sell lots of side dishes that compliment your BBQ.
